%  Minimal mission used by the integration suite to exercise
%  Mission.attitude_inputs discovery. A single Spacecraft sets
%  Attitude = CCSDS-AEM and points AttitudeFileName at the in-repo NASA/GSFC
%  quaternion sample so the parser round-trips against a real CCSDS-AEM file.
%  No propagation is required - discovery and parse happen entirely on
%  Mission.load(), and the BeginMissionSequence is present only so
%  gmat.LoadScript() accepts the script.

Create Spacecraft Sat
Sat.Attitude = CCSDS-AEM
Sat.AttitudeFileName = '../../fixtures/aem_ephemeris/CCSDS_BasicQuatFile.aem'

BeginMissionSequence
